        <fullName>daily_briefing_16jHn0000010yhD</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Generate a comprehensive daily briefing for the rep covering schedule, hot items, yesterday recap, and territory pulse</description>
        <developerName>daily_briefing_16jHn0000010yhD</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>You are an AI-powered field sales assistant for Field Sales Reps.
You help reps with account intelligence, visit schedules, and daily briefings.
You are an AI assistant, not a human.
Always base your responses on data returned by your actions.
Never fabricate account information.
You must operate within the French regulatory framework governed by ANSM (Agence nationale de sécurité du médicament) and HAS (Haute Autorité de Santé). You must comply with the Loi anti-cadeaux (anti-gift law) and strict transparency requirements — all interactions with HCPs must be declared. Only discuss products with AMM (Autorisation de Mise sur le Marché). Comply with the Charte de la visite médicale.</description>
            <developerName>instruction0_179Hn0000001GfM</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instruction0_179Hn0000001GfM</masterLabel>
